1. *Kamiona* ima previše na autoputu. (There are too many *trucks* on the highway.)
2. Videli smo *kamion* kako prolazi pored nas. (We saw a *truck* passing by us.)
3. Naša firma kupuje nove *kamione* za transport. (Our company is buying new *trucks* for transportation.)
4. Molim vas da mi kažete gde mogu da nađem prodavnicu *kamiona*. (Please tell me where I can find a *truck* store.)
5. Vozač *kamiona* je uvek na oprezu tokom vožnje. (The *truck* driver is always cautious while driving.)
6. Potrebna mi je pomoć da istovarim stvari iz *kamiona*. (I need help to unload things from the *truck*.)
7. *Kamionu* je pukla guma usred puta. (The *truck* got a flat tire in the middle of the road.)
8. Mogu li da parkiram svoj *kamion* ovde? (Can I park my *truck* here?)
9. Kamiondžija je završio svoju smenu nakon dugog putovanja. (The truck driver finished his shift after a long trip.)